full_text:
Blitz updates: Offensive performance against the blitz when you're likely to run vs when you're likely to pass. San Fran is killing it. We'll see if they maintain their top spot without Jimmy G. Lions have been blitzed 160 times!! Miami only 82. 

#nflverse #rstats https://t.co/5eQlyY04wZ

Now defenses when blitzing. Titans have only blitzed 76 times (2nd lowest), but have been very efficient with them. Giants have blitzed on 196 snaps! And been mediocre. Miami has faced the fewest, but blitzed the 3rd most. Seattle should probably stop trying. 

#nflverse #rstats https://t.co/zCCqF4xvkL
